1 A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
2 AN ACT TO ENACT THE NORTH CAROLINA UNIFORM ELECTRONIC WILLS ACT; TO
3 MAKE UPDATES TO THE ELECTIVE SHARE STATUTES; TO UPDATE STATUTES
4 RELATING TO TRUST ADMINISTRATION; AND TO MAKE REVISIONS TO THE
